ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
SubjectDirected Sales of Unleased, Surplus Lands and the Removal of Conditions of Sale for la Maison de l'Union des Producteurs Agricoles, in Mirabel, Quebec
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the concession to Her Majesty of real and perpetual right-of-way servitudes by destination of the owner, which will be imposed on federal immovables situated in the vicinity of the Montreal-Mirabel International Airport; and (2) authorizing the Minister of Transport to sign any deed of servitude related to the concession of a right-of-way servitude.
